node.text:
I have exciting news to share with you: Spain is back!

The restaurants, the museums, the vineyards, the beaches, the bars and more…so much more! They’re all open and waiting for YOU!

node.text:
Cuando fundamos @wckitchen, soñé con un mundo donde un plato caliente de comida llevara alimento, esperanza y empatía en tiempos difíciles... Hoy, me siento honrado de que seamos reconocidos con este premio. No es para mi, sino para todos los que hacen posible este trabajo. Nunca dejaremos de cocinar! 

When we founded @wckitchen, I dreamed of a world where a hot plate of food would bring nourishment, hope, and empathy in hard times…Today, I am humbled we are recognized with this Award. It is not for me, but for everyone who makes the work possible. We’ll never stop cooking!
